You're lucky to be traveling in a place with a spring so handy.

730
00:38:51,950 --> 00:38:55,320
在我那兒  連續幾天都看不到一滴水
In my country you can ride for days and see no ground water.

731
00:38:55,890 --> 00:38:58,390
