Maybe, maybe this is true.

740
00:39:17,610 --> 00:39:20,640
說不定舔髒水是騎警隊的規定
Maybe lapping water off the ground is Ranger policy.

741
00:39:20,640 --> 00:39:23,050
你太無知了  考伯恩
You're getting ready to show your ignorance now, Cogburn.

742
