是啊  沒錯
Yes, that is the way!

753
00:39:50,900 --> 00:39:53,440
你弄得我在小姑娘眼  顯得特蠢
Make me out foolish in this girl's eyes.

754
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,380
