某種協議吧
some sort of agreement.

765
00:40:54,080 --> 00:40:55,300
作為你的僱主
And as your employer I believe

766
00:40:55,310 --> 00:40:56,980
我有權知道  詳細內容
I have the right to know the particulars.

767
00:40:57,180 --> 00:40:58,180
