What's going on?

793
00:42:00,430 --> 00:42:02,490
我們在談生意
This is a business conversation.

794
00:42:02,490 --> 00:42:03,570
談生意
Is that what you call it?

795
00:42:03,570 --> 00:42:06,340
看起來  你還是被小姑娘擺佈
Sounds to me you're still being hoorawed by a little girl.

796
00:42:06,340 --> 00:42:08,360
-你說  擺佈  -沒錯
