797
00:42:08,360 --> 00:42:10,760
沒有擺佈  我和警官的協議
There is no hoorawing in it. In my agreement with the Marshal,

798
00:42:10,760 --> 00:42:12,470
比你的早  這有法律效應的
antedates your. It has the force of law.

799
