01:20:02,110 --> 01:20:03,360
和帕克法官
and Judge Parker's court.

1344
01:20:09,510 --> 01:20:11,680
我要把你帶回史密斯堡
I have come to take you back to Fort Smith.

1345
01:20:17,420 --> 01:20:19,110
我不去
Well I will not go.

1346
01:20:19,110 --> 01:20:20,110
你覺得怎麼樣
How do you like that?

1347
01:20:20,120 --> 01:20:23,300
那邊有一治安團的警官會抓你去的
There is a posse of officers up there who will force you to go.

1348
01:20:23,750 --> 01:20:25,590
有意思
That is interesting news.

1349
01:20:25,590 --> 01:20:26,760
那邊有多少人
And how many is up there?

1350
01:20:27,250 --> 01:20:28,530
五十個左右
Right around fifty.

1351
01:20:28,940 --> 01:20:30,780
他們都武器精良  志在必得
They're all well armed and they mean business.

1352
01:20:31,490 --> 01:20:32,820
現在我要你渡過小溪
What I want you to do now is come on across the creek

1353
01:20:32,820 --> 01:20:34,790
從我面前走到那座山上去
and walk in front of me up that hill.

1354
01:20:35,520 --> 01:20:38,880
我還是讓那些警官來抓我吧
I think I will oblige the officers to come after me.

1355
01:20:39,690 --> 01:20:41,790
如果你不照著做  我就得開槍了
Well if you refuse to go, then I'll have to shoot you.

1356
01:20:42,460 --> 01:20:43,460
噢
Oh.

1357
01:20:43,460 --> 01:20:45,730
那你最好給槍上膛
Well you had better cock your piece.

1358
01:20:48,050 --> 01:20:49,090
一直向後扳
All the way back.

1359
01:20:50,410 --> 01:20:52,670
-直到鎖住  -我知道怎麼做
- Til it locks. - I know how to do it.

1360
01:20:53,340 --> 01:20:54,610
你不打算跟我走?
You will not go with me?

1361
01:20:54,610 --> 01:20:56,100
不  恰恰相反
Naw, it's just the other way around.

1362
01:20:56,100 --> 01:20:57,350
你得跟我走
You're going with me.

1363
01:20:57,920 --> 01:20:58,920
我要...
I will...AAAH!

1364
01:21:08,170 --> 01:21:10,240
我沒想到你會開槍
I did not think you would do it.

1365
01:21:10,240 --> 01:21:13,580
-現在呢  -我有根肋骨斷了
- What do you think now? - One of my short ribs is broken.

1366
01:21:13,580 --> 01:21:15,990
我爸爸想幫助你  你卻殺了他
You killed my father when he was trying to help you.

1367
01:21:16,410 --> 01:21:17,190
我有一個你從他那偷的金幣
I have one of the gold pieces you stole from him.

1368
01:21:17,190 --> 01:21:18,310
現在把另一個也給我
Now give me the other.

1369
01:21:18,610 --> 01:21:20,610
-我幹什麼都不順  -麥蒂
- Nothing has gone right for me. - MATTIE!

1370
01:21:20,610 --> 01:21:22,080
我在這下面
I'm down here.

1371
01:21:22,080 --> 01:21:23,700
現在居然被個孩子打中了
Now I'm shot by a child.

1372
01:21:23,700 --> 01:21:25,300
我抓住切尼了
Chaney is taken into custody!

1373
01:21:31,840 --> 01:21:32,840
快救我
Help me.

1374
01:21:32,840 --> 01:21:33,870
麥蒂
Mattie!

1375
01:21:36,810 --> 01:21:37,810
警官
Marshal.

1376
01:21:44,760 --> 01:21:45,990
把馬牽上  快走
Take them horses you got and move!

1377
01:21:52,010 --> 01:21:54,610
湯姆  到那山上去  別停下
Tom, get on up that hill! Don't you stop..

1378
01:21:58,320 --> 01:21:59,410
下面都是些什麼人
Who all is down there?

1379
01:21:59,430 --> 01:22:01,380
考伯恩和其他五十個警官
Marshal Cogburn and fifty more officers.

1380
01:22:07,820 --> 01:22:10,220
再敢撒謊  我打穿你的頭
Tell me another lie and I will stove your head in!

1381
01:22:10,750 --> 01:22:12,250
只有一個法警
Just the Marshal.

1382
01:22:13,970 --> 01:22:15,410
大公雞
Rooster.

1383
01:22:17,520 --> 01:22:18,550
考伯恩
Cogburn!

1384
01:22:19,130 --> 01:22:20,390
聽得見嗎
You hear me?

1385
01:22:23,630 --> 01:22:25,270
回答我  大公雞
You answer me, Rooster!

1386
01:22:26,450 --> 01:22:28,010
我要殺了這姑娘
I will kill this girl!

1387
01:22:28,400 --> 01:22:29,720
你知道我幹得出來
You know I will do it!

1388
01:22:31,460 --> 01:22:32,890
她對我來說什麼也不是  
The girl is nothing to me!

1389
01:22:32,890 --> 01:22:34,790
只是個阿肯色州來的亡命者
She is a runaway from Arkansas!

1390
01:22:34,790 --> 01:22:36,540
非常好
That is all very well.

1391
01:22:36,790 --> 01:22:38,940
你建議我把她殺了嗎
Do you advise that I kill her?

1392
01:22:41,730 --> 01:22:43,550
隨你的便  奈德
Do what you think is best, Ned.

1393
01:22:43,550 --> 01:22:46,270
她只不過是個迷路的小孩
She's nothing to me but a lost child.

1394
01:22:49,380 --> 01:22:50,680
先好好想想
Think it over first.

1395
01:22:50,680 --> 01:22:52,620
我已經好好想過了
I have already thought it over!

1396
01:22:52,800 --> 01:22:55,060
這樣你會過來得更快
You get mounted double fast!

1397
01:22:55,060 --> 01:22:58,480
如果看到你越過那座禿山  向西北去
If I see you riding over that bald ridge to the northwest,

1398
01:22:58,480 --> 01:22:59,910
我就放了這姑娘
I will spare the girl.

1399
01:23:00,620 --> 01:23:02,150
給你五分鐘
You have five minutes!

1400
01:23:02,150 --> 01:23:04,930
馬上就會有一隊法警過來  奈德
There will be a party of marshals here soon, Ned!

1401
01:23:04,930 --> 01:23:06,520
把這姑娘和切尼交給我
Let me have the girl and Chaney

1402
01:23:06,520 --> 01:23:09,500
我就把他們引開六個小時
and I will mislead them for six hours!

1403
01:23:09,500 --> 01:23:11,240
太不夠意思了  大公雞
Too thin, Rooster!

1404
01:23:11,240 --> 01:23:12,290
太不夠意思
Too thin!

1405
01:23:12,990 --> 01:23:14,720
五分鐘已經快到了
Your five minutes is running!

1406
01:23:14,720 --> 01:23:16,310
別再說了
No more talk!

1407
01:23:19,790 --> 01:23:21,230
到那山上去
Get on up that hill.

1408
01:23:23,530 --> 01:23:25,230
安靜
Quiet there!

1409
01:23:32,660 --> 01:23:34,950
法雷爾  看看湯姆的傷口
Farrel, see to Tom's wound.

1410
01:23:35,320 --> 01:23:36,950
我能來點培根嗎
Can I have some of that bacon?

1411
01:23:36,950 --> 01:23:38,040
隨便你
You help yourself.

1412
01:23:38,550 --> 01:23:39,910
再來點咖啡
Have some of the coffee.

1413
01:23:39,910 --> 01:23:42,130
我不喝咖啡  我才十四歲
I do not drink coffee, I am fourteen.

1414
01:23:42,830 --> 01:23:46,010
我們可沒有酸奶  也沒有麵包
Well we do not have buttermilk, and we do not have bread.

1415
01:23:46,410 --> 01:23:47,880
我們補給不足
We are poorly supplied.

1416
01:23:47,880 --> 01:23:49,710
-她在哪兒  -你在這媟F嘛
- Where she is. - What are you doing here?

1417
01:23:49,710 --> 01:23:51,460
我要擰斷你的小細脖子
I will ring your scrawny neck.

1418
01:23:51,470 --> 01:23:52,540
別提這茬了
You let that go.

1419
01:23:54,770 --> 01:23:56,130
怎麼回事
What happened, huh?

1420
01:23:56,140 --> 01:23:58,500
我告訴你  你就會明白我佔理了
I will tell you and you will see that I'm in the right.

1421
01:23:58,500 --> 01:24:00,660
湯姆·切尼在史密斯堡槍殺了我爸爸
Tom Chaney there shot my father to death in Fort Smith

1422
01:24:00,660 --> 01:24:01,740
還搶了他兩個金幣
and robbed him of two gold pieces

1423
01:24:01,740 --> 01:24:03,570
偷了他的牝馬
and stole his mare.

1424
01:24:03,690 --> 01:24:04,890
我聽說考伯恩先生很有種
I was informed Rooster Cogburn had grit

1425
01:24:04,890 --> 01:24:06,880
就雇他來抓捕兇手
and I hired him out to find the murderer.

1426
01:24:07,150 --> 01:24:09,930
剛才我正好看到切尼在飲馬
A few minutes ago I came upon Chaney watering the horses.

1427
01:24:09,940 --> 01:24:11,890
他不服法  我便朝他開槍了
He would not be taken in charge and I shot him.

1428
01:24:12,720 --> 01:24:14,400
如果我把他打死
If I had killed him

1429
01:24:14,400 --> 01:24:17,200
現在就不會被抓住  可我的槍啞火了
I would not be now in this fix. My revolver misfired.

1430
01:24:17,280 --> 01:24:18,320
是這樣
They will do it.

1431
01:24:18,900 --> 01:24:20,640
啞火總是會讓你陷入窘境
It will embarrass you every time.

1432
01:24:21,360 --> 01:24:24,570
姑娘們都玩娃娃  可你喜歡槍  是嗎
Most girls like to play pretties, but you like guns, do ya?

1433
01:24:24,570 --> 01:24:26,400
我對槍一點興趣都沒有
I do not care a thing in the world about guns.

1434
01:24:26,400 --> 01:24:27,910
如果有的話  我就會有支好使的槍了
If I did I would have one that worked.

1435
01:24:27,910 --> 01:24:29,840
我中了埋伏  奈德
I was shot from ambush, Ned.

1436
01:24:29,840 --> 01:24:31,490
馬在打響鼻  不斷發出噪音
The horses was blowing and making noise.

1437
01:24:31,490 --> 01:24:32,800
是警官打中我的
It was that officer that got me.

1438
01:24:32,810 --> 01:24:34,940
你怎麼還能在那大言不慚
How can you sit there and tell such a big story?

1439
01:24:34,940 --> 01:24:37,690
那個坑有一百英尺深  我要把你扔進去
That pit is a hundred feet deep, and I will throw you in it.

1440
01:24:37,690 --> 01:24:39,940
讓你尖叫著腐爛
I'll leave you screaming in rot.

1441
01:24:39,940 --> 01:24:41,810
-現在你覺得怎麼樣  -你不會的
- Now how do you like that? - No you won't.

1442
01:24:41,810 --> 01:24:43,110
這個人不會讓你為所欲為的
This man will not let you have your way.

1443
01:24:43,110 --> 01:24:44,730
他是你老闆  你得照他說的做
He's your boss and you have to do as he tells you.

1444
01:24:45,920 --> 01:24:47,610
我從來都沒法為所欲為
Ain't nothing going my way.

1445
01:24:48,410 --> 01:24:50,740
前天晚上埋伏我們的人是大公雞嗎
Was that Rooster waylaid us night before last?

1446
01:24:50,740 --> 01:24:52,440
是考伯恩警官和我
It was Marshal Cogburn and myself.

1447
01:24:52,820 --> 01:24:54,100
你和考伯恩
You and Cogburn.

1448
01:24:55,030 --> 01:24:56,320
真厲害
Quite the posse.

1449
01:25:14,770 --> 01:25:16,070
咱們走吧  奈德
Let us move, Ned.

1450
01:25:16,070 --> 01:25:17,400
時機到了再走  醫生
In good time, Doctor.

1451
01:25:17,860 --> 01:25:19,440
昆西和那孩子怎麼樣了
What happened to Quincy and the kid?

1452
01:25:21,950 --> 01:25:22,990
他們都死了
They are both dead.

1453
01:25:24,630 --> 01:25:27,050
我當時身歷其境  太可怕了
I was in the very middle of it. It was a terrible thing to see.

1454
01:25:27,130 --> 01:25:28,980
拜託  我們走吧  奈德
Please, let us move, Ned.

1455
01:25:28,990 --> 01:25:30,520
法警已經走了
The Marshal's gone.

1456
01:25:30,520 --> 01:25:31,820
你需要好的律師嗎
Do you need a good lawyer?

1457
01:25:32,350 --> 01:25:33,900
我需要好的法官
I need a good judge.

1458
01:25:34,880 --> 01:25:36,470
寇可·海斯怎麼樣了
What happened to Coke Hayes,

1459
01:25:36,470 --> 01:25:38,080
這老傢伙被從馬上射下來了
the old fellow shot off his horse.

1460
01:25:38,450 --> 01:25:39,820
也死了
Dead as well.

1461
01:25:40,610 --> 01:25:42,470
這些暴行已經結束了
These depredations have come to an end.

1462
01:25:43,140 --> 01:25:45,980
你朋友大公雞活捉不了幾個人
Your friend Rooster does not collect many prisoners.

1463
01:25:45,980 --> 01:25:47,210
他不是我的朋友
He is not my friend.

1464
01:25:49,410 --> 01:25:51,760
他把我扔給了一群野蠻人
He has abandoned me to a congress of louts.

1465
01:25:52,020 --> 01:25:53,990
你從不掩飾你的想法嗎
You do not varnish your opinions.

1466
01:25:54,860 --> 01:25:56,040
我們出發嗎
Are we off?

1467
01:25:56,040 --> 01:25:58,580
咱們把飛之凱蒂那票賺的分了吧
Let us cut up the winnings from the Katie Flyer.

1468
01:25:58,580 --> 01:26:00,410
到老地方再分也來得及
They'll be time for that at the old place.

1469
01:26:00,690 --> 01:26:01,960
我騎那匹灰的
I will mount the grey.

1470
01:26:01,960 --> 01:26:03,210
你有別的任務
I have other plans for you.

1471
01:26:03,210 --> 01:26:05,330
我得和醫生騎一匹馬嗎
Must I double-mount with the Doctor?

1472
01:26:05,330 --> 01:26:06,650
-不  -不
- No! - Nope.

1473
01:26:06,660 --> 01:26:08,970
逃跑的話  兩人騎一匹馬太冒險了
Too chancy with two men up if it comes to a race.

1474
01:26:09,190 --> 01:26:10,920
湯姆  你和這姑娘待在這兒
Tom, you wait here with the girl.

1475
01:26:11,040 --> 01:26:12,890
到老馬家後我會派卡羅爾
When we reach Ma's house I will send Carroll back

1476
01:26:12,900 --> 01:26:14,250
帶新馬回來
with a fresh mount.

1477
01:26:14,250 --> 01:26:15,620
你天黑出發
You will be out by dark

1478
01:26:16,250 --> 01:26:17,490
我們在老地方見
and we'll meet you at The Old Place.

1479
01:26:17,490 --> 01:26:19,100
我不想這樣
I do not like that.

1480
01:26:19,200 --> 01:26:22,440
讓我和你一起走  奈德  離開這再說
Let me ride with you, Ned. Just out here anyway.

1481
01:26:22,440 --> 01:26:23,640
缺一匹馬
I was short a horse.

1482
01:26:23,640 --> 01:26:25,310
這媟|來大批法警的
Marshals will come swarming.

1483
01:26:25,310 --> 01:26:26,900
得有段時間呢  如果他們真來的話
Hours, if they come here at all.

1484
01:26:27,020 --> 01:26:28,530
他們會以為我們都走了
They'll think that we've all gone.

1485
01:26:28,530 --> 01:26:31,040
我不要一個人和湯姆·切尼在一起
I am not staying here by myself with Tom Chaney.

1486
01:26:31,260 --> 01:26:32,510
就這麼定了
That's the way I will have it.

1487
01:26:32,510 --> 01:26:33,630
他會殺了我的
He will kill me.

1488
01:26:33,640 --> 01:26:35,600
你聽見他說了  他已經殺了我爸爸
You heard him say it. He's killed my father,

1489
01:26:35,600 --> 01:26:37,080
現在你還要讓他殺了我
and now you will let him kill me.

1490
01:26:37,300 --> 01:26:38,790
他不會這麼幹的
He will do no such thing.

1491
01:26:38,940 --> 01:26:41,830
湯姆  你知道柏林路口吧
Tom, you know the crossing at Cypress Forks,

1492
01:26:41,830 --> 01:26:43,540
圓木禮拜堂附近那個
near the log meetinghouse?

1493
01:26:43,850 --> 01:26:46,280
到那兒的時候  你把這姑娘留下
When you mount it, you take the girl and leave her there.

1494
01:26:46,550 --> 01:26:47,850
明白了嗎  湯姆
You understand, Tom?

1495
01:26:48,040 --> 01:26:50,470
你敢動這小妹妹一根皮毛
Any harm comes to that child,

1496
01:26:50,970 --> 01:26:52,100
你就拿不到錢
you do not get paid.

1497
01:26:54,770 --> 01:26:57,400
哈羅德  讓我和你騎一匹吧
Harold, let me ride up with you.

1498
01:26:58,320 --> 01:27:01,670
哈羅德  我從我那份堨I五十塊錢給你
Harold, I will pay you fifty dollars out of my winnings!

1499
01:27:01,680 --> 01:27:03,150
我不重的
I am not heavy.

1500
01:27:03,480 --> 01:27:05,270
再學個牛叫  哈羅德
Do the calf again, Harold.

1501
01:27:33,280 --> 01:27:34,820
事事都跟我作對
Everything is against me.

1502
01:27:35,600 --> 01:27:37,160
你沒理由抱怨
You have no reason to whine.

1503
01:27:38,180 --> 01:27:39,800
你按強盜頭子的話做
If you act as the bandit chief instructed,

1504
01:27:39,800 --> 01:27:42,460
不傷害我  就能在老地方拿到報酬
and no harm comes to me, you will get your winnings at The Old Place.

1505
01:27:42,750 --> 01:27:43,880
狗屎運奈德扔下我一個人
Lucky Ned has left me,

1506
01:27:43,880 --> 01:27:46,550
他知道我只能步行的話肯定會被抓的
knowing I am sure to be caught when I leave on foot.

1507
01:27:47,390 --> 01:27:50,250
得考慮怎麼逃出生天了
Must think over my position and how I may improve it.

1508
01:27:50,720 --> 01:27:53,040
另一個加州金幣在哪兒
Where's the second California gold piece?

1509
01:27:55,770 --> 01:27:57,120
你把爸爸的馬怎麼樣了
What have you done with Papa's mare?

1510
01:27:57,120 --> 01:27:58,410
安靜
Keep still.

1511
01:27:59,120 --> 01:28:00,910
你是在猜測老地方在哪兒嗎
Are you thinking about the old place?

1512
01:28:01,320 --> 01:28:03,370
聽著  如果你放了我
Look here, if you let me go

1513
01:28:03,370 --> 01:28:04,790
我就寫書面證詞
I will swear to an affidavit

1514
01:28:04,790 --> 01:28:08,730
你上法庭的時候會有利於你
and once you are brought to justice, it may go easier on you.

1515
01:28:10,160 --> 01:28:12,200
告訴你  我能做得更好
I tell you I can do better than that.

1516
01:28:18,570 --> 01:28:20,690
我不需要書面證詞
I need no affidavit.

1517
