Some bully shot.

1562
01:32:07,200 --> 01:32:09,250
至少有四百碼
That was four hundred yards at least.

1563
01:32:12,310 --> 01:32:14,360
夏普斯卡賓槍  是...
the Sharps carbine, is a...

1564
01:32:28,760 --> 01:32:30,480
站起來  湯姆·切尼
Stand up, Tom Chaney.

1565
01:33:07,250 --> 01:33:09,720
勒波義夫先生
M...Mr. LeBoeuf!

1566
01:33:14,100 --> 01:33:15,340
