Are you alive?

1567
01:34:28,590 --> 01:34:29,950
勒波義夫先生
Mr. LeBoeuf!

1568
01:34:34,820 --> 01:34:36,420
勒波義夫先生
Mr. LeBoeuf!

1569
01:34:38,240 --> 01:34:39,640
勒波義夫先生
Mr. LeBoeuf!

1570
01:34:43,390 --> 01:34:44,390
你在那兒嗎
Are you there?

1571
01:34:45,430 --> 01:34:46,430
我在這
I'm here.

1572
01:34:46,430 --> 01:34:47,850
你能爬出來嗎
Can you clamber out?

1573
01:34:48,080 --> 01:34:49,080
不能
I cannot.

1574
01:34:49,080 --> 01:34:50,570
這有蛇
There are snakes!

1575
01:34:50,570 --> 01:34:51,840
醒著的嗎
They awake?

1576
