不  停下
No, stop.

1604
01:38:16,950 --> 01:38:18,360
他逃跑了
He's getting away.

1605
01:38:18,850 --> 01:38:20,110
誰逃跑了  小妹妹
Who's getting away, sis?

1606
01:38:21,330 --> 01:38:22,330
切尼
Chaney.

1607
01:38:57,920 --> 01:38:59,470
不  不
No.. NO!

1608
