很遺憾告訴您  您錯過了大公雞
It grieves me to tell you that you have missed, Rooster.

1640
01:42:33,370 --> 01:42:35,770
他三天前去世了
He passed away three days ago.

1641
01:42:35,770 --> 01:42:38,230
演出團那時在阿肯色州的瓊斯伯勒
When the show was at Jonesboro Arkansas.

1642
