We too had, lively times.

1649
01:43:07,490 --> 01:43:08,820
謝謝你  揚戈先生
Thank you, Mr. Younger.

1650
01:43:11,470 --> 01:43:13,170
繼續坐著吧  醉鬼
Keep your seat, trash.

1651
01:43:15,460 --> 01:43:16,850
我把他的遺體運回故地
I had the body removed to our plot

1652
01:43:16,850 --> 01:43:19,360
多年來常去祭拜
and I had visited it over the years.

1653
