They say, "Well, she hardly knew the man".

1656
01:43:29,990 --> 01:43:32,190
"她是個神志不清的老處女吧"
"Isn't she a cranky old maid".

1657
01:43:33,180 --> 01:43:35,550
確實  我沒結婚
It is true, I have not married.

1658
01:43:35,550 --> 01:43:37,470
